citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 8:55AM on 12-May-
2022. The inspector knocked at the residence, called the licensee and left a voicemail and waited 30 minutes at the
premises.
End Section
